<p>Choose a title for your conversation (Make it descriptive, maybe provocative, but most of all, it should make sense)</p>
<fieldset class="form-group">
  <%= form.label :title %>
  <%= form.text_field :title %>
</fieldset>

<p>Choose an image to go with your conversation (it will look best if you choose one with a 3:2 ratio—wide, not tall)</p>
<fieldset class="form-group">
  <%= form.label :image %>
  <%= form.file_field :image %>
</fieldset>
<br class="clear" />

<p>Give us a short description of what you want to accomplish in this conversation. (By "short," we mean about 250 characters, or two sentences.)</p>
<fieldset class="form-group">
  <%= form.label :summary %>
  <%= form.text_area :summary, :rows => 5 %>
</fieldset>

<p>Just so we know where you are, what’s your zip code?</p>
<fieldset class="form-group">
  <%= form.label :zip_code, "Zip Code" %>
  <%= form.text_field :zip_code %>
</fieldset>
